rows.label: qst104903_msg0001
rows.name:
Ooh... A handsome gentleman,
holding beautiful ice flowers,
coming towards me...

rows.label: qst104903_msg0003
rows.name:
Just, just a moment~ An
idea is coming to me...

rows.label: qst104903_msg0004
rows.name:
I'd like to thank you, but I
need a little more time...

rows.label: qst104903_msg0005
rows.name:
No! I cannot have a handsome
gentleman work for free!

rows.label: qst104903_msg0006
rows.name:
I have a room at the
Anastasis inn in Teos Aure.
Could you visit me there?

rows.label: qst104903_msg0101
rows.name: Have you brought me the ice flowers?

rows.label: qst104903_msg0102
rows.name:
They are such beautiful flowers...
I'd really prefer to receive them
from a handsome gentleman~~
